Host *.cirrostratus.org
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa
    StrictHostKeyChecking no
    User scoffman
    IdentitiesOnly yes
    UseKeychain yes
    AddKeysToAgent yes

Host *01.test *02.test *03.test *04.test *01.prod *02.prod *03.prod *04.prod
    HostName %h.cirrostratus.org
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa
    StrictHostKeyChecking no
    User scoffman
    IdentitiesOnly yes
    UseKeychain yes
    AddKeysToAgent yes

